<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
		<div style="font-size:20px;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold">Please do not reply to this email!</div>
    <h4>Reminder for the upcoming event: <%= @event.name %></h4>
    <p>This is a friendly reminder that the date for the event is <%= @event.display_start_time %>. </p>
		<p><%= link_to 'View event or edit RSVP', event_url(@event, :auth_token => @attendee.authentication_token) %></p>

		<p>You may also login to <%= link_to 'Lets Gather', root_url %> if you have an account. You may also contact your host at <%= @event.user.email %> for any further inquiries.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>

